item.title: About me
item.author: alanyin6@gmail.com (AlanYin)
item.description: About AlanYin If you refresh yourself each day, every day seems new. Hey, I’m AlanYin,a programmer who loves to explore new things. Aside from work and study, I’m also an avid reader and enjoy outdoor activities. I consider myself fortunate to be born in this era of information and to have chosen a profession I love. Living in this opportune time, my goal is to continually grow, keep pace with the times.
